# Bundled runtime output — generated by stage_runtime_mac.sh
# Contains ~1GB of Python packages (torch, demucs, etc.)
# Run ./stage_runtime_mac.sh to regenerate.
# No trailing slash on the second line (unlike the first): a trailing "/"
# only matches a real directory, not a symlink — a worktree may have this as
# a symlink into the main checkout's staged runtime (agent-worktree.py's
# fixture copier doesn't know about this dir, so a session that needs the
# bundled Python here symlinks it in for local execution). Found 2026-07-17
# when exactly that symlink showed up untracked instead of ignored.
BundledRuntime/
BundledRuntime
__pycache__/
*.pyc
